cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.GR 

This paper deals with object detection and classification in street-view imagery, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves generating images using a deep learning framework, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of this method is relevant to autonomous driving (cs.RO) and asset management (cs.GR).
